==============================================================
Revision history for Perl extension Log::Dispatch::FileShared.
==============================================================

1.01
Initial version

1.02
Bumped version up in order to repackage module with the version
number as part of the directory name as required for creating a
FreeBSD port.

1.03
* Fixed issue with file not being truncated.
* Fixed issue where forked processes would close file handle and truncate
if first log didn't happen until inside child process.
